The Lagos State government has placed a ban on motorcycles and tricycles popularly known as ‘okada’ and ‘keke,’ in various local government areas of the state.
In the restriction order seen by National Daily, the government asked motorcycle and tricycle operators to refrain from operating on major roads in Lagos.
See full list of restricted roads
